snippet: Second seed Andy Murray advanced into the second round of the Australian Open after a comfortable 6-1 6-2 6-3 victory over Germany's Alexander Zverev on Tuesday....
lead_paragraph: Second seed Andy Murray advanced into the second round of the Australian Open after a comfortable 6-1 6-2 6-3 victory over Germany's Alexander Zverev on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Murray Proves Too Strong for Bloodied and Beaten Zverev
